message.entry: OBJ must be a 1-by-1 VISA-PXI, VISA-VXI or VISA-GPIB-VXI object.
OBJ must be an interface object.
MEMREAD is supported for VISA-PXI, VISA-VXI and VISA-GPIB-VXI objects.
Invalid OFFSET specified. OFFSET must be finite.
Invalid OFFSET specified. OFFSET must be greater than or equal to 0.
Invalid OFFSET specified. OFFSET must be a scalar.
Invalid SIZE specified. SIZE must be finite.
Invalid SIZE specified. SIZE must be greater than 0.
Invalid SIZE specified. SIZE must be a scalar.
Invalid ADRSPACE specified. ADRSPACE must be ''PXICFG'', ''BAR0'', ''BAR1'', ''BAR2'', ''BAR3'', ''BAR4'' or ''BAR5''.
Invalid ADRSPACE specified. ADRSPACE must be ''A16'', ''A24'' or ''A32''.
Invalid PRECISION specified. PRECISION must be ''uint8'', ''uint16'', ''uint32'' or ''single''.
